Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:04.20,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Dareno kimagure kara sekai sae mo owarisoude}You feel like someone's careless\Nact could end the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break in 2 the nite" It's that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:09.73,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Obieta me wo shite lost in the night}Lost in the night with frightened eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:13.39,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{ochiteku yume ni dakareru}Embraced by a ruined dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:17.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kodoku ga kowakute missin' my heart}Scared of loneliness, I'm missing you in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:20.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{jibun sae mo kizu tsukete}I almost hurt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:24.54,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Taoreru kurai ni love me so much}Love me so much and knock me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:28.23,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{subete wo suttee anata wo}If only I can give up everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.89,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ai suru koto sae dekitara}...and love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:36.13,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{kitto sunao ni naresou}...I can be my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...I'm so happy to be here, Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's wonderful and gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:14.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here, and let's go\Nswimming together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:23.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}We're coming!{\r}\NWe're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be here, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.27,0:02:36.23,MainStyle,,0030,0000,0345,,{\fad(960,1000)}{\2a&HFF&}The End of Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, right, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NIsn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,S...sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi, let's go try the Slider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I'll just stay and relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:57.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's always out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind us going too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Together, together!{\r}\NTogether, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takumi, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:12.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't like the Slider...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can someone who can do\Nsuch a super drift say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:22.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuki's so forceful.\NAnd she's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:26.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay.\NThey're having fun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:30.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for everyone\Nto take the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We begged to take a paid\Nvacation day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager didn't look\Ntoo happy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She's so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My heart is almost bursting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}At least I've gotten to see\Nher in a bathing suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:55.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...so this'll be the greatest memory\Nof my 21st summer of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:06.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}After all, Mako is beyond my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to thank you for a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:18.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot from that race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:26.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I caused you a lot of trouble,\Nbut I won't quit racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\NThat's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:37.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I got conceited because they put\Nthe label of Usui's fastest on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}No, you can't recover!\NJust spin to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:03.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I needed to learn a lot\Nmore about controlling a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:10.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I quit racing now, I'd leave\Nsomething unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So something good came\Nout of what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:28.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the promise\Nwe made by the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:35.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have misunderstood\Nbecause of the way I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I wasn't trying to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:45.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you... to be my first man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:56.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you in front of the signboard\Nwhere we first met around 8:00 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I feel her breasts on my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I feel something on my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako, get the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Please!{\r}\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi Ryosuke...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, Sayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you throwing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Why does she have a picture\Nof Takahashi Ryosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,N...no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:51.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you've never had a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've had a crush or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:05.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why you can't\Ngo out with that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:09.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Most guys would be attracted\Nto you because of your looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.  That'll never happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what kind of man is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:21.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... a Road Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:29.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I was still in high school,\Nso it was about three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:37.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Some senior schoolmates\Ntook me to watch a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know anything at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the way one car went by shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:51.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His driving looked clearly different from\Nthe others, even to my amateur eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:57.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked by this unknown world... and I was\Nfascinated by the world of Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:13.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my license right after that, and then\NI worked hard to buy a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that I would be able\Nto get close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My motivation sounds silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:37.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone to see his driving quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:53.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I don't know if I can call it love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:58.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether I liked\Nhim or his driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But... you liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I liked him so much.{Hiro:  Past tense, past tense, Iketani.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:13.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What... is this pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:15.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She seems so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:32.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So her crush was on the superstar\Nof the Gunma area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:42.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Now I know why she likes FCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm no match for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:26.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Finally, my brother has decided to race\Nagainst Akina's Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming with me, Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:37.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my hypothesis\Nfor the fastest driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:49.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:53.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew going to the pool\Nwith girls was this fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:58.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were with Kenji\Nalmost all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:05.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako and Sayuki are great, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your recovery is quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to say that Road Racers\Ndon't need girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still see those two\Nin their bikinis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:32.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuki's bouncy boobs are amazing,\Nbut it's Mako after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:35.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a knockout bod,\Ndon't you think, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with your reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fight with Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:51.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.\NI'm just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the matter\Nat this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about today.\NI asked too much of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:09.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're young, so you\Nneed to have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:14.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be worried if you were only into\Ncars and didn't have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:21.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako is your angel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:28.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:33.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beyond my reach after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Iketani, girls are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:42.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Manager.\NI've already given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no match for Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What's happened?  I'm barely\Nkeeping up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:09.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}His FC hasn't been changed, so why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:28.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My hypothesis for the fastest driving\Nis refined every time I get new data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Wait for me, Eight-Six of Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:37.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}As soon as I've completed it, I'll put\Nyour name on the list of losers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0400,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Kamameshi Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:09.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I arrived before he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My chest feels tight.\NMy heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If I'm like this now, I don't know what\NI'll do when Iketani shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or what, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:25.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "Eh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If she was actually going out with Takahashi\NRyosuke, you'd be out of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but young girls have those\Nkinds of feelings, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:39.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no different than\Ndreaming about TV stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down, and think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:47.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she chose you over\NTakahashi Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...she took courage and\Nmade up her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:54.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she believes in you,\Nshe told you how she feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:59.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your inferiority\Ncomplex hold you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:04.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,To love someone means to\Naccept everything about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:08.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what loving and caring\Nis all about, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Eight o'clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, you're thirty minutes late already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take at least one hour to get to Yokokawa\Nno matter how fast I drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:46.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:51.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know unless you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't go, I'll fire you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:13.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Road Racer, this is\Nthe time to drive like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:20.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But having said that... I don't\Nthink he can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's part of being young...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:39.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The manager is right.\NHow could I be so stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:50.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll never have another chance\Nto meet someone like Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Why couldn't I be honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'm Sato Mako.  Call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:03.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'll give you my virginity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:09.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'll be waiting for you in front of the signboard\Nwhere we first met around 8:00 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:14.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Mako is always serious, but I...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate... sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:15.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Mako, I'm not expecting to go\Nto a hotel or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:23.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No! I just want to see her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:29.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Please, God!  Give me one more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Don't take my angel away from my world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Traffic jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:41.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}An accident... at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:52.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No... God, this is so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:03.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Sorry, Mako...
